{"timestamp": "2025-12-12 12:03:12.292427", "event": "llm_end", "text": "**Problem Summary**\n\n* **Host 10.1.1.10 (host_1_1_1_1)**  \n  * Default gateway set to **10.1.1.1**.  \n  * Pings to **10.1.1.1** fail with “Network is unreachable”.  \n  * Consequently, all traffic to the 10.200.0.0/24 subnet (web servers, load‑balancer, DHCP, etc.) is either unreachable or times‑out.  \n  * Only the DNS server (10.200.0.2) is reachable, and even that shows 25 % packet loss.\n\n* **Gateway 10.1.1.1**  \n  * No device in the topology is configured with IP 10.1.1.1.  \n  * The nearest device that could serve as a gateway is **switch_access_1_1_1** (br0/eth0/eth1).  \n  * That switch is a bridge/bridge‑only device – it has no IP address and no routing table, so it cannot forward packets to the 10.200.0.0/24 network.\n\n* **Router_core_1**  \n  * Has a route to 10.1.1.0/24 via 172.16.0.7 on eth2, but that route is never used because the host never reaches its own gateway.\n\n**Root Cause**\n\nThe host’s default gateway (10.1.1.1) is missing or mis‑configured. The device that should provide that gateway is either not powered on, not configured with an IP address, or is a pure bridge that cannot route traffic. Because the host cannot reach its gateway, all packets destined for the 10.200.0.0/24 subnet are dropped or mis‑routed, leading to the observed “Network is unreachable” and time‑outs.\n\n**Key Findings**\n\n1. **Gateway unreachable** – host_1_1_1_1 cannot reach 10.1.1.1.  \n2. **Missing IP on gateway device** – switch_access_1_1_1 has no IP address configured.  \n3. **Partial connectivity to DNS** – the single reachable host (dns_server) shows 25 % loss, indicating that some packets are being routed but the path is unstable.\n\n**Conclusion**\n\nThe network connectivity problem originates from a missing or incorrectly configured default gateway (10.1.1.1). Fixing the gateway’s IP configuration or replacing the device will restore full connectivity to the 10.200.0.0/24 subnet.", "generation_info": {"model": "gpt-oss:20b", "created_at": "2025-12-12T12:03:11.269632043Z", "done": true, "done_reason": "stop", "total_duration": 21854403260, "load_duration": 61338861, "prompt_eval_count": 7624, "prompt_eval_duration": 6707219032, "eval_count": 1277, "eval_duration": 12274192601, "model_name": "gpt-oss:20b"}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7624, "output_tokens": 1277, "total_tokens": 8901}}
